title: Synthesis of quinoxalines and assessment of their inhibitory effects against human non-small-cell lung cancer cells
content:
RSC Adv., 2024, 14,28659-28668
DOI: 10.1039/D4RA04453C, Paper

Jia-Hua Liang, Shu-Tse Cho, Tzenge-Lien Shih, Jih-Jung Chen
Twenty-six quinoxalin derivatives were synthesized to assess their biological activities against human non-small-cell lung cancer cells (A549 cells). Among them, compound 4m exhibited the most potent inhibitory activity against A549 cells.
